# Inventory System — Cursor Agent Rules

> **All rules live in `_agent/rules.md`.** Read that file, not this one.

## Quick Start

1. Read `_agent/rules.md` — rules, file index, common mistakes
2. Read `_agent/context/patterns.md` — code templates (when writing code)
3. Use diffs only — never rewrite entire files
4. Build every 2-3 files — `npm run build`
5. If stuck after 3 attempts — stop and ask

## Critical Rules (summary)

1. All DB queries through `lib/dal/` — never import Prisma elsewhere
2. Auth: `requireCurrentUser()` from `lib/dal/guards.ts`
3. DAL returns typed DTOs — never raw Prisma models
4. Actions: `"use server"` → Zod → DAL → `revalidatePath`
5. Catch blocks: `catch (error: unknown)` + `handleServerError(error)`
6. No `any` types — use `unknown` and proper types
7. `type` not `interface` for DTOs
